## Vendored Components Notice

This product includes software developed by third parties:

### @open-multi-agent/core (vendored under vendor/open-multi-agent/)

Copyright (c) 2025 open-multi-agent contributors

Licensed under the MIT License. A copy of the upstream LICENSE is preserved at
`vendor/open-multi-agent/LICENSE`. Upstream source: https://github.com/open-multi-agent/open-multi-agent

The vendored copy is unmodified at the time of vendoring. Local modifications
applied via `patch-package` are recorded in `patches/`. To upgrade the
vendored copy, run:

```bash
npm install @open-multi-agent/core@<new-version>
npx patch-package @open-multi-agent/core
```